Emission factor represents direct combustion emissions from vehicle operation. Obtained from GREET 2023 Fuel-cycle Model, this pathway represents SPK (HRJ). GREET assumes carbon neutrality from biomass-derived fuels, meaning that CO2 emissions from combustion are offset by CO2 uptake by plants.
